When you reach certain Barbarian levels, you gain the ability to use the mastery properties of more kinds of weapons, as shown in the Weapon Mastery column of the Barbarian Features table. (2 at level 2, 3 at level 4, 4 at level 10)

Source:	Player's Handbook 2024 p. 52</text>
