Temporary Hit Points:
As a Magic action, you can give yourself a number of Temporary Hit Points equal to 1d8 plus your Wisdom modifier (minimum of 1). You can use this action a number of times equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum of once), and you regain a ll expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.

Decrease Exhaustion:
Whenever you finish a Short Rest, your Exhaustion level, if any, decreases by 1.

