Core Artificer Traits
• Primary Ability: Intelligence
• Hit Point Die: D8 per Artificer level
• Saving Throw Proficiencies: Constitution, Intelligence
• Armor Training: Light Armor, Medium Armor, Shields
• Weapon Proficiencies: Simple weapons
• Tool Proficiencies: Thieves' Tools, Tinker's Tools, Artisan's Tools of your choice
